### ==========================================
### ERROR TEST CASES
### ==========================================

### Error Test 1: Unauthorized Access (No Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/1

###

### Error Test 2: Invalid Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/1
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

###

### Error Test 3: Non-existent User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Error Test 4: Non-existent Product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Error Test 5: Insufficient Stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/carts/items
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 10000
}

###

### Error Test 6: Invalid Email Format (Registration)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

###

### Error Test 7: Weak Password (Registration)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "weakpass@example.com",
  "password": "weak",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

###

### ==========================================
### BULK OPERATIONS (Sequential Tests)
### ==========================================

### Bulk Test 1: Complete User Journey
### 1. Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "journey@example.com",
  "password": "JourneyPassword123!",
  "firstName": "Journey",
  "lastName": "Tester",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

> {%
  if (response.status === 201) {
    client.global.set("journeyUserId", response.body.id);
    console.log("User registered: " + response.body.id);
  }
%}

###

### Bulk Test 2: Complete Purchase Journey
### 1. Login and get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
  if (response.status === 200) {
    client.global.set("journeyToken", response.body.token);
  }
%}

###

### Bulk Test 2 (cont): 2. Add to cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/carts/items
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{journeyToken}}

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### Bulk Test 2 (cont): 3. Create order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{journeyToken}}

{
  "shippingAddress": "456 Oak Ave, Springfield, IL 62701"
}

> {%
  if (response.status === 201) {
    client.global.set("journeyOrderId", response.body.id);
  }
%}

###

### Bulk Test 2 (cont): 4. Process payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{journeyToken}}

{
  "orderId": {{journeyOrderId}},
  "amount": 599.98,
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "cardToken": "tok_visa_4242424242424242"
}

###

### ==========================================
### PERFORMANCE TEST - Concurrent Requests
### (Uncomment to test)
### ==========================================

