### ==========================================
### USAGE INSTRUCTIONS
### ==========================================

# To use this file:
# 1. Install VS Code Extension: REST Client (humao.rest-client)
# 2. Replace {{baseUrl}} with your API URL
# 3. Click "Send Request" or use Ctrl+Alt+R (or Cmd+Alt+R on Mac)
# 4. Login first to get the {{token}} variable
# 5. Use the token in subsequent requests

# Variables are set in responses with:
# > {%
#   client.global.set("variableName", value);
# %}

# Comments:
# Single line: #
# Multiple lines: ### (creates request separator)

# Tips:
# - Click "Send Request" in editor (CodelLens link appears above request)
# - View responses in a new tab
# - Use "Generate Code Snippet" to convert to other languages
# - Share requests.http file with team via Git
